com.groep6.pfor.util

Class Vector2f

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.groep6.pfor.util.Vector2f

  • public class Vector2f
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a vector in 2d space. Has mathematical applications but is also useful to wrap two float together, mostly used for coordinates.
    Author:
    Owen Elderbroek
